attack against selective disclosure for <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">the past 18 months</TIMEX>, and <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">yesterday</TIMEX> the
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">SEC</ENAMEX> issued a remarkably measured proposal, <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Regulation FD</ENAMEX>, that simply stated in
