and brokerage <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">houses</ENAMEX> built their <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">businesses</ENAMEX> around their access to information,
and their ability to get that information to their <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">clients</ENAMEX> before it reached
